name: HMI Shapes Library
description:
IF im=Non Standard then
 Calculated Hrs = 2 * ss + 6 * ms + 10 * cs + 16 * vcs + 0.5 * rs
Else If im= Standard build and GES=None then
 Calculated Hrs = (2 * ss + 6 * ms + 10 * cs + 16 * vcs + 0.5 * rs) * 0.7
Else If GES!=None and im= Standard build  then
Calculated Hrs = (2 * ss + 6 * ms + 10 * cs + 16 * vcs + 0.5 * rs) * 0.7 * 1.2
